{"tid":1639973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多澳門手足係支持我地？","createTime":"2019-10-08T19:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T00:45:36.000Z","uid":225569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1e04d663d62bbbb2cd8ffe7e39d9257d8668bdda","tid":1639973,"uid":225569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:56:53.000Z","msg":"我本人有好多澳門朋友，同學。發覺唔少後生嘅居然係藍色。都底有幾多澳門手足係支持我地，點解又會有咁多藍絲，你地係點諗？"},{"pid":"c2a672f8ffa6b557ddcc2b99bff8630132b90404","tid":1639973,"uid":225569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:00:49.000Z","msg":"我知澳門都好多問題，你地有冇諗過反抗？同香港connect?"},{"pid":"7bca756ee8df0adbbd61fabefe9d31eadaf144b9","tid":1639973,"uid":224561,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016afd9a08cfa33205356178f10d71ef4a242b2f","tid":1639973,"uid":78762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:05:10.000Z","msg":"好多我哋呢一代都Connet咗<br />\n不過佢哋地方奶共做唔到啲咩嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9594f767b7e0207a1d756c15df7084370b81dc3d","tid":1639973,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:06:51.000Z","msg":"澳門一早比中共控制左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早幾十年澳門警察都已經好似公安咁<br />\n返工hea下玩下警棍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb6ac02253839b694b7f4a20167c432f5096893","tid":1639973,"uid":33073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:09:59.000Z","msg":"10萬個應該有1個嘅。<br />\n<br />\n利申:10幾個澳門親戚，得一個自稱中立，其他全部紅底。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1289d30e37d4c110da89290fc5ae104dc5599ae6","tid":1639973,"uid":221913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c486